      <title>进口量下降导致德国昂贵的液化天然气终端建设未能带来回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/germany-s-costly-lng-terminals-aren-t-paying-off-as-imports-dip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国投入巨资建设液化天然气终端以确保能源安全，但使用成本高昂，意味着它们只能满足其天然气需求的一小部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/germany-s-costly-lng-terminals-aren-t-paying-off-as-imports-dip</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 14:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
